I've only now come to visit you.

45
00:04:01,140 --> 00:04:03,800
In the past, I told you...

46
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:08,580
I didn't want to become a general.

47
00:04:08,580 --> 00:04:11,960
I wanted to be a swordsman who freely roams the Martial World.

48
00:04:13,380 --> 00:04:15,100
Now...

49
00:04:19,100 --> 00:04:21,500
I'm halfway there.

50
00:04:24,660 --> 00:04:26,910
I didn't bring anything good

51
00:04:27,430 --> 00:04:29,940
to see you today.

52
00:04:32,780 --> 00:04:35,340
Let me show you some swordplay.

53
00:05:14,500 --> 00:05:16,160
Father.

54
00:05:16,900 --> 00:05:18,500
Mother.

55
00:05:18,500 --> 00:05:20,310
Wait for me...

56
00:05:21,100 --> 00:05:27,720
to clear your grievances.

57
00:05:41,100 --> 00:05:42,740
Come on.

58
00:05:43,900 --> 00:05:45,580
Pick a jar.

59
00:05:45,580 --> 00:05:47,800
One is not enough.

60
00:05:50,020 --> 00:05:51,640
You...

