♫  The rain from the mountains comes and the wind blows hard ♫

62
00:06:07,740 --> 00:06:11,260
♫  The red candle moves and the shadows flicker ♫

63
00:06:11,260 --> 00:06:15,060
♫  Everyone's an enemy, gracefully and ready to fly ♫

64
00:06:15,060 --> 00:06:19,260
♫  The world is in chaos, there's instability, Heaven and Earth gather  ♫

