69
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:35,860
What... What martial art is this?

70
00:06:35,860 --> 00:06:37,980
This is the internal strength you're about to learn.

71
00:06:37,980 --> 00:06:41,551
It's called the Falling Flowers and Flowing Water. 
  (TN: lit. to be utterly defeated)

72
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:45,420
Falling Flowers and Flowing Water?

73
00:06:45,420 --> 00:06:47,300
♫  The heart is like algae floating on the waves  ♫

74
00:06:47,300 --> 00:06:49,300
♫  I'm all alone  ♫

75
00:06:49,300 --> 00:06:55,780
♫  The obsession can't be returned  ♫

76
00:06:56,980 --> 00:07:01,460
It seems this person is the one who snuck into the Academy in broad daylight.

77
00:07:01,460 --> 00:07:03,900
Such splendid skills.

78
00:07:06,700 --> 00:07:09,300
How can you still appreciate his martial arts?

79
00:07:09,300 --> 00:07:13,460
Baili Dongjun was targeted by various people as soon as he entered the city.

80
00:07:13,460 --> 00:07:16,060
No, I have to check on him.

81
00:07:19,620 --> 00:07:21,060
It's indeed good liquor.

82
00:07:21,060 --> 00:07:24,160
It's a pity to waste a couple of drops.

83
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:30,200
It's a hidden weapon. Old Seven, let's go and deal with him.

84
00:07:31,700 --> 00:07:33,340
What hidden weapon?

85
00:07:33,340 --> 00:07:36,140
It's just a drop of liquor.

86
00:07:36,140 --> 00:07:39,380
Rest assured, this person means no harm.

87
00:07:39,380 --> 00:07:43,200
He just greeted us a moment ago.

88
00:07:43,200 --> 00:07:45,620
What does that mean? Do...

89
00:07:45,620 --> 00:07:47,100
Do you know him?

90
00:07:47,100 --> 00:07:51,230
Wait, why didn't you tell me that you know him?

91
00:07:51,230 --> 00:07:52,920
Who is he?

92
00:07:54,860 --> 00:07:56,680
I brought Baili Dongjun here.

93
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:59,900
- Why are you more anxious than me? 
 - I was—

94
00:08:01,820 --> 00:08:04,240
He is the Chief of Baixiao Hall, Ji Ruofeng.

95
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:05,960
He's an old acquaintance of Scholarly Deity's.

96
00:08:05,960 --> 00:08:09,600
He's willing to teach Baili Dongjun Scholarly Deity's Autumn Water Technique.

97
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:13,800
Did you think I'd ask Dongjun to learn the Lei Clan's clumsy internal strength technique?

98
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:17,340
- I-I... 
 - Then he wouldn't pass the Academy's exam in 10 years.

99
00:08:17,340 --> 00:08:19,000
Am I...

100
00:08:23,220 --> 00:08:24,980
Am I clumsy?

101
00:08:28,820 --> 00:08:31,940
From now on you'll give me five jars of liquor for every visit.

102
00:08:31,940 --> 00:08:34,900
- How about that? 
 - Don't overdo it.

103
00:08:34,900 --> 00:08:37,100
You can brew more when the liquor runs out.

104
00:08:37,100 --> 00:08:41,600
But if you fail the Academy exam, there won't be another chance.

105
00:08:44,020 --> 00:08:48,560
It seems the liquor I brew is really too good.

106
00:08:49,300 --> 00:08:52,100
Come on. Although there isn't much time left,

107
00:08:52,100 --> 00:08:55,820
it shouldn't be a big problem for you.

108
00:09:16,940 --> 00:09:20,660
Young Master, there are only three days left until the preliminary exam.

109
00:09:20,660 --> 00:09:25,900
Have you finished writing the exam questions?

110
00:09:25,900 --> 00:09:29,680
Didn't you already say the exam is in three days?

111
00:09:29,680 --> 00:09:31,460
Why are you in such a hurry?

112
00:09:31,460 --> 00:09:34,140
I'm not in a hurry. Why would I be in a hurry?

113
00:09:34,140 --> 00:09:36,780
- I just think that maybe we... 
 - Why?

114
00:09:36,780 --> 00:09:40,660
Everyone is afraid to ask me directly so they pressure you instead?

115
00:09:40,660 --> 00:09:42,340
Am I right?

116
00:09:42,340 --> 00:09:45,780
It's really exhausting for anyone when they ask three or four times a day.

117
00:09:45,780 --> 00:09:50,400
In previous years, there were hints given seven days before the preliminary exam.

118
00:09:50,400 --> 00:09:54,540
Are you really going to wait until the last day to announce it this time?

119
00:09:54,540 --> 00:09:58,160
Isn't it normal procedure to announce it on the last day?

120
00:09:58,160 --> 00:10:01,740
Why? Has the Academy become shameless now?

121
00:10:01,740 --> 00:10:06,720
Is leaking exam questions in advance an unspoken rule now?

122
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:11,800
Liuyue, the preliminary exam doesn't determine the final result.

123
00:10:11,800 --> 00:10:14,060
There's still a final examination after the preliminary exam.

124
00:10:14,060 --> 00:10:17,140
The finals, which involve teams competing against one another,  have remained unchanged for decades.

125
00:10:17,140 --> 00:10:19,240
That is where the candidates true strengths are tested.

126
00:10:19,240 --> 00:10:23,580
The preliminary exam is just for the young men to bring home some good omens.

127
00:10:23,580 --> 00:10:26,400
Don't take it so seriously, Liuyue.

128
00:10:27,180 --> 00:10:28,980
Young Master Zhuomo is right.

129
00:10:28,980 --> 00:10:31,740
With Young Master Liuyue's talent,

130
00:10:31,740 --> 00:10:34,040
even if the exam questions were disclosed in advance,

131
00:10:34,040 --> 00:10:39,000
- it would still be pointless if the candidates have no abilities. 
 - That's right.

132
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:40,980
Why are you talking so much nonsense?

133
00:10:40,980 --> 00:10:44,020
- Do you still want to play? 
 - No.

134
00:10:44,020 --> 00:10:46,300
I can't win against you anyway.

135
00:10:47,380 --> 00:10:49,680
I was just wondering...

136
00:10:49,680 --> 00:10:54,880
why you would suddenly come to play GO with me today and humiliate yourself.

137
00:10:54,880 --> 00:10:57,680
It turns out you also came for the exam questions.

138
00:10:59,120 --> 00:11:03,080
Well, I brought a friend here who is preparing for the exam.

139
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:06,800
Besides, I could find out the questions 10 days in advance in previous years.

140
00:11:06,800 --> 00:11:10,040
Who knew you would be the chief examiner this time?

141
00:11:11,380 --> 00:11:13,220
Excellent, really excellent.

142
00:11:13,220 --> 00:11:16,260
That's why I'm visiting you personally.

143
00:11:16,900 --> 00:11:21,200
- What if I insist on announcing the questions on the last day? 
 - Fine.

144
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:25,240
It seems you'll be the chief examiner every year from now on.

145
00:11:25,820 --> 00:11:29,120
- Are you threatening me? 
 - Yes, I'm threatening you. So what?

146
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:31,480
You do know I'm very talkative.

147
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:33,320
I'll go to Master every day and sway him.

148
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:36,900
I'll tell him you are an excellent chief examiner.

149
00:11:36,900 --> 00:11:42,240
I'll keep persuading him until he gets annoyed and agrees to make you the chief examiner every year.

150
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:44,660
- Fine. 
 - Year after year.

151
00:11:44,660 --> 00:11:46,900
I surrender.

152
00:11:58,370 --> 00:12:00,100

153
00:12:00,100 --> 00:12:02,860
Beyond civil and military.

154
00:12:03,620 --> 00:12:06,620
That's right. It's Beyond Civil and Military.

155
00:12:06,620 --> 00:12:09,740
Major exams in the world are divided into civil and military categories.

156
00:12:09,740 --> 00:12:13,400
But there are so many interesting things beyond these two categories.

157
00:12:13,400 --> 00:12:18,660
So I won't test civil or military subjects.

158
00:12:18,660 --> 00:12:21,540
So long as this topic has something that impresses me,

159
00:12:21,540 --> 00:12:25,740
I'll let them pass the preliminary exam.

160
00:12:26,520 --> 00:12:28,500
This is worse than saying nothing.

161
00:12:28,500 --> 00:12:31,860
But what exactly is tested if it has nothing to do with civil or military subjects?

162
00:12:31,860 --> 00:12:36,940
You need to know that our academy not only seeks people who excel in both these skills,

163
00:12:36,940 --> 00:12:39,880
but also those who are interesting.

164
00:12:39,880 --> 00:12:44,580
My topic is to test the candidates themselves.

165
00:12:49,220 --> 00:12:53,760
Liuyue. You're giving me special treatment here.

166
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:56,120
Don't pin that on me.

167
00:12:56,120 --> 00:13:02,200
What I said was from the bottom of my heart, and has nothing to do with your friend.

168
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:03,940
I got it.

169
00:13:06,500 --> 00:13:12,140
By the way, how is that young man doing?

170
00:13:12,140 --> 00:13:17,200
I have no idea. I haven't seen him in days.

171
00:13:44,960 --> 00:13:50,320
That feels great. Having internal strength sure makes a big difference.

172
00:13:53,900 --> 00:13:55,640
Is Lei Mengsha at the Academy today?

173
00:13:55,640 --> 00:13:58,820
How would I know Young Master Zhuomo's whereabouts?

174
00:13:58,820 --> 00:14:01,220
Where are your manners?

175
00:14:01,220 --> 00:14:04,020
What's up? Do you need something from me today?

176
00:14:04,020 --> 00:14:05,780
I have good news for you.

177
00:14:05,780 --> 00:14:10,080
- What a coincidence. I have good news for you too. 
 - Really? You go first.

178
00:14:12,880 --> 00:14:14,980
Listen.

179
00:14:14,980 --> 00:14:16,540
The topic for the preliminary exam is out.

180
00:14:16,540 --> 00:14:19,500
It is? What's the topic?

181
00:14:19,500 --> 00:14:21,500
Four words.

182
00:14:21,500 --> 00:14:26,660
Beyond Civil and Military.

183
00:14:37,500 --> 00:14:42,220
What's wrong? Are you so happy you're stunned? That expression...

184
00:14:49,660 --> 00:14:56,240
Wait. With your mediocre civil and military skills, Beyond Civil and Military" is quite a good topic.

185
00:14:56,240 --> 00:14:58,680
Beyond Civil and Military?

186
00:14:58,680 --> 00:15:02,220
I've been practicing martial arts for days and now you say Beyond Civil and Military is the topic?

187
00:15:14,900 --> 00:15:17,140
This is so irritating!

188
00:15:26,320 --> 00:15:31,760
This is ridiculous. Beyond Civil and Military isn't testing civil or military skills. How's this an examination?

189
00:15:31,760 --> 00:15:33,680
Then what do you think is being tested?

190
00:15:33,680 --> 00:15:37,280
Maybe whoever looks the best gets into the final exam?

191
00:15:37,280 --> 00:15:42,060
You make a good point. Young Master Liuyue is said to be extraordinarily handsome.

192
00:15:42,060 --> 00:15:46,420
Maybe it really is whoever looks the best meets the requirements.

193
00:15:46,420 --> 00:15:48,920
That young man is very handsome.

194
00:15:48,920 --> 00:15:52,160
If he takes the exam, he will surely pass.

195
00:15:52,160 --> 00:15:54,800
He indeed has an extraordinary presence.

196
00:15:54,800 --> 00:15:57,600
- Thank you for the compliments. 
 - You're most welcome.

197
00:15:57,600 --> 00:16:01,580
Beyond Civil and Military. That's pretty interesting.

198
00:16:20,430 --> 00:16:23,680

199
00:16:27,300 --> 00:16:30,760
Welcome, Miss. Winter will be here soon. Our shop just received a new selection of fabrics.

200
00:16:30,760 --> 00:16:33,100
Owner, make me a set of clothes.

201
00:16:33,100 --> 00:16:35,780
It's urgent. I want them within three days.

202
00:16:35,780 --> 00:16:37,340
Sure.

203
00:16:38,660 --> 00:16:41,880

204
00:16:48,380 --> 00:16:54,630

205
00:17:02,030 --> 00:17:04,170

206
00:17:07,540 --> 00:17:09,360
That's enough.

207
00:17:14,420 --> 00:17:17,840
Young Master Liuyue, you always do things in your own way.

208
00:17:17,840 --> 00:17:24,280
This is the first time I've heard of holding the academy's exam in a gambling house.

209
00:17:25,300 --> 00:17:29,320
The so-called exam is actually no different from gambling.

210
00:17:29,320 --> 00:17:31,160
Please elaborate.

211
00:17:31,160 --> 00:17:35,060
Many people have studied hard for ten years for this exam.

212
00:17:35,060 --> 00:17:38,400
It might be the moment for them to create the best performance

213
00:17:38,400 --> 00:17:43,280
or perhaps perform badly with no chance of redemption.

214
00:17:43,280 --> 00:17:45,800
Gambling is the same.

215
00:17:45,800 --> 00:17:49,540
Until you sit at the gambling table no one knows what will happen.

216
00:17:49,540 --> 00:17:54,080
Once you're at the table, the game has just begun.

217
00:17:54,080 --> 00:17:56,280
Well said!

218
00:17:56,280 --> 00:17:58,960
Unless you're cheating.

219
00:17:58,960 --> 00:18:04,680
Why? Someone dares to cheat at Qianjin Gambling House?

220
00:18:04,680 --> 00:18:06,960
Of course not.

221
00:18:06,960 --> 00:18:09,920
That's why we're holding the exam here today.

222
00:18:09,920 --> 00:18:14,580
Young Master Liuyue. You are indeed extraordinary.

223
00:18:14,580 --> 00:18:18,140
Marvelous, truly marvelous.

224
00:18:19,300 --> 00:18:23,020
Even my golden tooth is in awe of you.

225
00:18:24,660 --> 00:18:28,600
Where's Second Master? Wasn't he the one who agreed to lend us this place?

226
00:18:28,600 --> 00:18:34,060
He went to listen to a song. I don't know why he likes listening to songs so much.

227
00:18:34,060 --> 00:18:37,280
He wasn't interested at all in the academy exam.

228
00:18:37,280 --> 00:18:42,940
He only agreed to let you use the place because Young Master Liuyue traded a piece of an old music score with him.

229
00:18:44,320 --> 00:18:51,140
Hosting the academy exam here means Qianjin Gambling House loses 10,000 taels of silver a day.

230
00:18:52,320 --> 00:18:54,140
I don't mind.

231
00:18:57,500 --> 00:19:02,320
Master Tu, your losses will be compensated by the Academy tomorrow.

232
00:19:03,860 --> 00:19:06,820
The Academy is really generous.

233
00:19:06,820 --> 00:19:10,440
Excellent. Generous. How nice.

234
00:19:14,820 --> 00:19:18,100
 We can do this!

235
00:19:18,100 --> 00:19:20,380
 We can do this!

236
00:19:21,380 --> 00:19:23,540
 We can do this!

237
00:19:30,400 --> 00:19:33,180
I, Young Master Baili Dongjun, am here.

238
00:19:35,480 --> 00:19:38,300
Who... Who is this?

239
00:19:38,300 --> 00:19:39,980
Who's this?

240
00:19:41,780 --> 00:19:44,900
- Drunk again? 
 - Who's—

241
00:19:46,820 --> 00:19:49,280
You are the expert from Swords Forest. You are—

242
00:19:49,280 --> 00:19:51,560
- Ye Dingzhi. 
 - That's right. You're Ye Dingzhi.

243
00:19:51,560 --> 00:19:56,020
I was drunk that day but I remember your sword technique was good. And you're quite interesting.

244
00:19:56,020 --> 00:20:00,380
I wanted to befriend you but my uncle took me away before I could say anything.

245
00:20:00,380 --> 00:20:02,840
It's not too late now.

246
00:20:03,700 --> 00:20:05,460
You're right.

247
00:20:05,460 --> 00:20:08,510
- Are you here to take the academy exam too? 
 - Of course.

248
00:20:08,510 --> 00:20:10,460

249
00:20:12,300 --> 00:20:16,700
Candidates! Enter immediately!

250
00:20:17,490 --> 00:20:18,460

251
00:20:18,460 --> 00:20:21,020
- You'll pass! 
 - You can do it!

252
00:20:21,020 --> 00:20:22,500
Let's go.

