 - Not really.

255
00:20:42,620 --> 00:20:44,820
Just relax.

256
00:20:44,820 --> 00:20:46,820
It's my first time here.

257
00:20:58,780 --> 00:21:02,940
Could this be the betting odds that Lei Mengsha told me about?

258
00:21:07,140 --> 00:21:09,100
What's this?

259
00:21:09,100 --> 00:21:13,180
