260
00:21:13,180 --> 00:21:16,700
It's to see who will win first place today.

261
00:21:18,720 --> 00:21:20,260
What does this mean?

262
00:21:20,260 --> 00:21:22,220
What does the "one thousand" next to my name mean?

263
00:21:22,220 --> 00:21:24,790

264
00:21:24,790 --> 00:21:26,680
Does it mean the larger the number, the stronger you are?

265
00:21:26,680 --> 00:21:32,100
What are you thinking? The larger the number, the fewer people bet on you. And your odds are higher.

266
00:21:32,100 --> 00:21:37,660
If someone bets one tael of silver on you and you win first place, he will win a 1,000 taels.

267
00:21:37,660 --> 00:21:40,900
But the chances are slim. No one would want to take that risk.

268
00:21:40,900 --> 00:21:45,520
Unlike me, I'm a popular choice with many people betting on me.

269
00:21:45,520 --> 00:21:48,020
So my odds are not...

270
00:21:48,970 --> 00:21:50,870

271
00:21:50,870 --> 00:21:55,540

272
00:21:56,860 --> 00:21:59,140
Wait, it's also 1,000?

273
00:21:59,140 --> 00:22:02,480
You can't even catch a peach thrown by a student from Affiliated Academy.

274
00:22:02,480 --> 00:22:06,220
Your odds could be nothing but 1,000.

275
00:22:09,460 --> 00:22:14,520
The odds at Qianjin House are determined by the number of bets being placed.

276
00:22:14,520 --> 00:22:19,220
I hope you won't mind, Young Master Liuyue.

277
00:22:20,120 --> 00:22:23,740
How could Young Master care about such trivial matters?

278
00:22:28,860 --> 00:22:30,500
Let's go.

279
00:22:33,380 --> 00:22:35,200
Let's begin.

280
00:22:39,820 --> 00:22:43,980
The academy exam is about to begin.

281
00:22:50,680 --> 00:22:54,440
The Beyond Civil and Military exam invites all of you to showcase talents

282
00:22:54,440 --> 00:22:57,760
