311
00:25:00,840 --> 00:25:03,500
Yes, Your Majesty.

312
00:25:03,500 --> 00:25:08,980
Baili Luochen's grandson, Baili Dongjun, is among the exam candidates.

313
00:25:08,980 --> 00:25:10,840
Why is he in Tianqi City?

314
00:25:10,840 --> 00:25:15,040
It was the Ninth Prince who brought him to Tianqi City.

315
00:25:15,040 --> 00:25:19,440
Is it possible the Ninth Prince also...

316
00:25:22,240 --> 00:25:24,880
You're overthinking it like Old Nine.

317
00:25:24,880 --> 00:25:27,240
I know my son well.

318
00:25:27,240 --> 00:25:32,600
He likely brought Baili Dongjun to Tianqi simply because he admired him.

319
00:25:32,600 --> 00:25:35,340
He wouldn't give that boy a hard time.

320
00:25:36,540 --> 00:25:42,140
On the contrary, if Baili Dongjun was in trouble, he'd risk his life to save him.

321
00:25:42,140 --> 00:25:44,360
I'm curious about that.

322
00:25:44,360 --> 00:25:48,640
I've always heard Baili Luochen's only grandson is a notorious playboy.

323
00:25:48,640 --> 00:25:53,780
But unexpectedly he suddenly mastered the Xichu's Sword Song.

324
00:25:53,780 --> 00:25:58,200
And I wonder how he caught the eye of Old Nine.

325
00:25:58,200 --> 00:26:04,060
Your Majesty, you seem to appreciate the Ninth Prince a lot.

326
00:26:05,240 --> 00:26:07,300
You spoke too much.

327
00:26:07,920 --> 00:26:10,120
Please forgive me, Your Majesty.

328
00:26:10,120 --> 00:26:13,720
Which other princes have gone to the Academy's exam?

329
00:26:13,720 --> 00:26:16,580
Prince Qing.

330
00:26:16,580 --> 00:26:18,820
Old Second?

331
00:26:20,858 --> 00:26:22,680
Never mind him.

332
00:26:22,680 --> 00:26:30,160
These little games they play aren't worth my concern.

333
00:26:45,490 --> 00:26:47,770

334
00:27:42,440 --> 00:27:45,220
Examiner, I wish to present my talent.

335
00:27:50,980 --> 00:27:52,520
So soon?

336
00:27:52,520 --> 00:27:56,200
What's your name? What are you submitting?

337
00:27:57,900 --> 00:28:00,400
I'm Duan Baiyi from Baiyi Sect.

338
00:28:00,400 --> 00:28:02,320
I've studied GO since childhood.

339
00:28:02,320 --> 00:28:06,760
What I intend to present for Beyond Civil and Military is my skill in GO.

340
00:28:06,760 --> 00:28:08,020
Very well.

341
00:28:08,020 --> 00:28:10,660
Please enlighten me, Young Master.

342
00:28:18,500 --> 00:28:21,600
You? You want to play with me?

343
00:28:21,600 --> 00:28:24,160
- How long have you studied GO? 
 - How long have you studied?

344
00:28:24,160 --> 00:28:29,600
Since I was seven, that makes it 17 years.

345
00:28:29,600 --> 00:28:33,600
I started learning at three. That makes it seven years.

346
00:28:34,420 --> 00:28:37,240
That's not a big gap. Let's begin.

347
00:28:43,500 --> 00:28:45,500
I'm undefeated when I play with black pieces.

348
00:28:45,500 --> 00:28:47,200
You start first.

349
00:28:48,060 --> 00:28:49,720
Sure.

350
00:29:43,740 --> 00:29:45,700
He said he was good at playing GO?

351
00:29:45,700 --> 00:29:48,100
He can't even win against a maidservant.

352
00:29:48,100 --> 00:29:49,680
Being able to persist for so long against Lingsu

353
00:29:49,680 --> 00:29:55,040
while Lingsu is the one playing with the black pieces shows more than just proficiency.

354
00:29:55,840 --> 00:29:58,300
After more than 10 years of hard practice...

355
00:30:00,080 --> 00:30:04,600
I have actually lost to...

356
00:30:05,920 --> 00:30:08,020
a maidservant.

357
00:30:08,820 --> 00:30:10,900
It appears to be a game of GO.

358
00:30:10,900 --> 00:30:14,580
