403
00:34:37,320 --> 00:34:41,080
What do you think this person's background is?

404
00:34:41,080 --> 00:34:45,540
Who in the entire court can sway those from the Marquis Zhenxi's Mansion?

405
00:34:45,540 --> 00:34:53,220
